O'Neal appeared on NBA Ballers and NBA Ballers: Phenom,[217] in the 2002 Discovery Channel special Motorcycle Mania 2 requesting an exceptionally large bike to fit his large size famed custom motorcycle builder Jesse James,[218] in the first Idol Gives Back in 2007,[219] on an episode of Fear Factor,[220] and on an episode of MTV's Jackass, where he was lifted off the ground on Wee Man's back.[221] O'Neal was a wrestling fan and made appearances at many WWE events.[222]
